This paper discusses a new paradigm for automatic compliance checking of data privacy regulations in heterogeneous data processing infrastructures. It involves the creation and enforcement of privacy policies using a formal policy language. This work is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including cybersecurity (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), software engineering (cs.SE), and computer systems and networking (cs.CY).
